In order to fulfill its responsibility of effectively overseeing
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">management</ENAMEX>, the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">board</ENAMEX> must have a thorough understanding of the
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">company</ENAMEX>, its business model and related risks, corporate culture,
