Current <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Financial Reporting Model Has Limited Value</ENAMEX> in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Today</TIMEX>'s
Business Environment
Some <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">participants</ENAMEX> agreed that financial statements are an
