generally agreed that there is a demand for both historical and
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">fair</ENAMEX> value reporting. However, <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">participants</ENAMEX> felt that <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">FASB</ENAMEX> needed
to better differentiate between the <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</NUMEX>. In that respect, some
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">participants</ENAMEX> felt that <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">FASB</ENAMEX> is marching toward a "fair value" path
