<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">auditors</ENAMEX> off the street" than the accounting <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">firms</ENAMEX> themselves. The
accounting <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">firms</ENAMEX> do remove "bad <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">auditors</ENAMEX>," but this is accomplished
without publicity so that their efforts are not well known.
